These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, writing, skydiving, video-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, ice-hockey, golf, surfing
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person who's sport is golf##8
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | video-games  | singing | skydiving | writing  |
| Sport   | lacrosse | golf   | surfing  | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, artichoke, carrot, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, security-guard, chef, electrician
1. the electrician is not to the left of the electrician##8
2. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
3. the person eating eggplant is the security-guard##1
4. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the manager##7
6. the chef is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
7. the manager is not to the left of the manager##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | carrot | artichoke          | cucumber | eggplant     |
| Job    | chef      | electrician | manager | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, dressmaker, analyst, accountant
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, musical, disaster
1. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the analyst##8
2. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the dancer##1
4. the dressmaker is in an even position##4
5. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
6. the dancer is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
7. the accountant is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | dancer | dressmaker | analyst     | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | disaster   | scientific | musical    |

