.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, salsa, electronic, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, biathlon, golf, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of classical is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
5. the fan of ambient is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
6. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
7. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | salsa         | classical   | ambient    |
| Sport         | biathlon | water-polo | golf | ice-hockey |

