.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, animation, martial-arts, horror
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, sailing, skiing, biathlon
1. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person watching animation movies##7
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching satire movies##7
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person who's sport is sailing##7
6. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
7. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | martial-arts | horror | satire    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | biathlon   | skiing   | sailing |

