3. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
5. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
7. the person eating cranberry is the fan of folk##1

