.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, coffee, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon, basketball, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person who's sport is basketball##7
3. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | milk      | coffee | hot-chocolate | 7up   |
| Sport      | rugby | basketball | water-polo  | biathlon |

