2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
3. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the software-developer##7
5. the electrician is not to the right of the pilot##8
6. the pilot is somewhere between the person who's sport is surfing and the electrician##7

.:: Answer ::.
