.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, salsa, rock, gospel
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski, bike, skateboard
1. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of gospel and the person driving the motorbike##2
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the fan of rock is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the fan of gospel is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
8. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | hip-hop | rock | salsa |
| Transport     | skateboard | jet-ski       | motorbike  | bike    |

