2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
3. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating zucchini is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is camping##2
6. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
7. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | pepper        | pomegranate | zucchini      | papaya    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | camping   | baking | fishing |

