3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
8. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up | hot-chocolate         | water    | mirinda       |
| Sport      | tennis | cricket | surfing | parkour |

