.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, pepper, mango, banana
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, musical, fantasy, drama
 1. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 2. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person eating mango##8
 3. the person eating raspberry is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating raspberry is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 9. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8
10. the person eating pepper is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper    | mango | raspberry | banana |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | drama  | fantasy     | musical    |

