.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cherry, garlic, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, board-games, fishing, cooking
1. the person eating garlic is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person eating garlic is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
6. the person eating cherry is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person eating zucchini##2
7. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | zucchini        | cherry | spinach | garlic |
| Hobby   | cooking | fishing | board-games   | magic-tricks    |

