.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, ferret, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, roller, airplane, bus
1. the owner of the turtle is not the person driving the airplane##6
2. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the turtle##7
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
6. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
7. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig  | turtle | rat  | ferret  |
| Transport   | subway | roller   | bus | airplane |

