.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, rat, rabbit, dog
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, boat, trike, tram
1. the person driving the boat is not the owner of the cat##6
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
4. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person driving the helicopter##7
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the tram and the owner of the rabbit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | rat    | dog | cat | rabbit |
| Transport   | boat | tram      | trike     | helicopter     |

 